data.description: Big price adjustment!  Come home to this homely property in a quaint subdivision in Mesquite. This four bedroom plus bonus room, two full bath home will surely delight anybody with spacious living rooms for entertaining and well laid out floorplan. Property comes with state-of-the-art smoke, carbon monoxide, water alarm with bed shaker-indicator. The new homeowner definitely has a canvas for design that will suit their vision and taste with this home. Easy access to I-20 and straight west on Cartwright Rd will be a high school. Appreciate the beauty of this property, see its potential for you, and make an offer!
